column4: How do I restore firefox-3.5 bookmarks from a  file: qtxfxpk.default/bookmarkbackups/bookmarks-2009-07-22.json

In firefox, go to the bookmarks tab , then Organise Bookmarks, there's an import/backup tab, select that and then it should just be a case of picking Restore and selecting the file you want to restore from
: "Unable to process the backup file."   -- I think installing firefox-3.5 mangled the bookmark files into something it can't read.
I'm not sure what to suggest with that error, I've not come across it before, hopefully somebody else in the channel can help you with it
